metadata.name: The NFT Yearbook Mintpass #1
metadata.description:
The NFT Yearbook Mintpass 
 A project brought to you by **Metaverse Publishing**, The NFT Yearbook is aimed at showcasing, celebrating, and recording the Year in NFTs for future Generations  
  The NFT Yearbook will be a true collectible in both the digital and real world with a beautiful high quality 420-page coffee table book as well as an Interactive Digital NFT Book 
 This Mintpass assigns to its owner the rights to mint one free NFT Yearbook NFT and claim the Physical copy of the NFT Yearbook that goes with it as well as any additional utilities that come with it.  
 Holders of Mintpasses will be given priority access on Mint day and will also be given additional Whitelist Access to mint extra copies should they wish. 
 The NFT Yearbook Mintpass NFT affords early access to the first ever NFT Yearbook, a project by **Metaverse Publishing.** 
 www.metaversepublishing.io
